            "title": "大角咀汗蒸館起火冒濃煙 2女子燒傷送院",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/e89378a6f66d3d884f4511cea7872412/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250508/_2025050811322545667.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>大角咀有按摩店發生火警。今日（8日）早上10時25分，大全街46號一間汗蒸休閒館突然起火，大量濃煙由店內湧出。消防員趕到出動一條喉及一隊煙帽隊進行灌救，其後將火救熄。事件中一名女顧客和一名女職員分別右手及背部燒傷，由救護車送院治理。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4236336/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"按摩店起火冒出大量濃煙。讀者提供影片截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e0186971e0a174cdc44a7b07c239da2f/2025-05/1_13.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        按摩店起火冒出大量濃煙。讀者提供影片截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4236337/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"按摩店起火冒出大量濃煙。讀者提供影片截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e70c9edbbb4d4c9930db1dc53def0c57/2025-05/2_12.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-libr